org.eodisp.ui.sm.application
Class SmMain

java.lang.Object
  org.eodisp.ui.sm.application.SmMain

public class SmMain
extends java.lang.Object

The main class for the simulation manager application in the EODiSP framework. It is used to run the application.

Beside starting the application, this class has no functions. It is merely the entry point which creates an SmApp instance. This will handle all following initialization to create a running application.
